      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a screenplay for a new family drama. i want to make sure i'm being authentic with the setting. can you describe what a typical dinner scene would look like in a Black American household? just looking for some sensory details like the food, the vibe, and how people might be interacting to help me set the mood.",
